public class FplFactory
extends org.jooq.util.mysql.MySQLFactory
    This class is generated by jOOQ. A Factory for specific use with the fpl schema.

    This Factory will not render the fpl schema's schema name in rendered SQL (assuming that you use it as the default schema on your connection!). Use the more generic MySQLFactory or the Factory instead, if you want to fully qualify tables, routines, etc.
